# Asset generation candidates — large PNGs from exploration runs.
# The manifest at .art/generated.json IS tracked; the candidate images
# themselves are local-only. Winners get copied to .art/anchors/ or
# assets/sprites/ which ARE tracked.
/.art/candidates/
/.art/temp/
